        public String getBaseConnectionId()
        Gets the baseConnectionId. network_type 'gre_tunnel' connections use 'base_connection_id' to specify the ID of a network_type 'classic' connection the tunnel is configured over. The specified connection must reside in the same transit gateway and be in an active state. The 'classic' connection cannot be deleted until any 'gre_tunnel' connections using it are deleted. This field only applies to and is required for network type 'gre_tunnel' connections.
